Coordinates - Class in com.github.dvdme.GeoCoordinatesLib
Geographical Coordinates Object Parses geographical coordinates in one of four formats: - degrees minutes seconds: 40º 26' 46'' N, 79º 58' 56'' W - degrees decimal minutes: 40º 26.767' N, 79º 58.933' W - decimal degrees: 40.446º N, 79.982º W - decimal: 40.446, 79.982
